addUniqueParticipants(address[],uint256[.details: Adds a list of AirDrop `participants` to the AirDrop module with custom token amounts for each participant.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without an owner. It won't be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
